implementation_notes:
Snapshot data join strategy:
```
// Option 1: Join on Date directly (snapshot dates must be 1st of month)
DateTable[Date] (1) → FactTable[SnapshotDate] (*)

// Option 2: Join on YearMonthKey (more robust)
// DateTable: "YearMonthKey", YEAR([Date]) * 100 + MONTH([Date])
// FactTable (M): Table.AddColumn(Source, "YearMonthKey",
//     each Date.Year([SnapshotDate]) * 100 + Date.Month([SnapshotDate]), Int64.Type)
DateTable[YearMonthKey] (1) → FactTable[YearMonthKey] (*)
```
